{"title":"钢花报春","authors":["金谷"],"dates":[{"year":1979,"month":2,"day":4}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢花报春〔外一首〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金谷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪朝多美呵，银装玉砌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高炉在天上盼这场大雪；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"此刻，冶金群英会上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"华主席正和代表们谈钢说"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三千万钢花报春，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"情怀是如此壮烈；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一亿吨重任在肩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们也决不会胆怯！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党的号召是前进动力，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快把钢铁的春天迎接，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迈开大步踏冰雪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明年呵，再向党报捷！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和时间赛跑人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"该怎样珍惜生命？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请问一问同时间赛跑的人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当年，他发明万能工具胎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一年顶四年，靠的是闹革新；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为什么跑在时间的前面？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他说大干是咱本分！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"寸金难买寸光阴呵——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二十八年，一百多项革新！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远坚持同时间赛跑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王崇伦才永葆青春……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春风又吹绿千山万岭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八亿神州旌旗奋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把工作重点转到四化上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党中央发出了庄严的进军"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"令！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战鼓催征哟，分秒必争，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敢同时间赛跑，才能战无不"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胜！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十二年走完新长征的路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四化未来美似锦……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":5,"page_end":5}